373
00:22:44,000 --> 00:22:46,000
Nanê genimî malê kes nake.
 
No one makes wheat bread at home.

374
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:49,000
Ke firnê. Nanê genimî berê dikir ser sêlê.
 
Only the bakery. They made wheat bread before on the
