564
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:49,000
Gundê Dimilya.
 
Dimilya village.

565
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:50,000
Gundê Dimilya.
 
Dimilya village.

566
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:51,000
Erê.
 
Yes.

567
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,000
Nêzîkî Meydankê?
 
Near Meydanke?

568
00:29:52,000 --> 00:29:54,000
Nêzîkî Meydankê.
 
Near Meydanke.

569
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,000
Ser seran.
 
Welcome.

570
00:29:55,000 --> 00:29:56,000
